'''I'att Armament''' was a company that manufactured armaments, mostly for the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. They were owned and operated by the grandparents of [[Tinian I'att Azur-Jamin|Tinian I'att]], based on [[Druckenwell/Legends|Druckenwell]].

I'att Armaments was in charge of a top-secret project to manufacture a new type of [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtrooper]] armor that could dissipate and absorb [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] bolts. After giving a demonstration of the product, Tinian's grandfather was killed for questioning an [[Imperial officer/Legends|Imperial officer's]] command. In the ensuing events, the factory was destroyed by Tinian's lover, [[Daye Azur-Jamin]], and the armor project met a fiery end.

Following this, I'att Armaments was [[Imperialization/Legends|imperialized]]. They were known to trade in the [[Ringali Shell]].

